

SpringBoot
RestController : CRUD
JPA : JPQL, Native SQL, @NamedQueries
H2 DB: DB connection

Database : H2 DB

SQL Queries : 

   
	Table will be created by JPA properties by running the application.
	
	data.sql --> DB File

application.properties 
	
	make  spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=create    only for first time for creating Books table in books_data datasource
	

Start up the application :
	1. Build and Run the application using Maven Build with   clean install spring-boot:run
	
	
	
application.properties 
	
	make  spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=none    and rerun the application after first time.
	
Url

	http://localhost:8080/books/getAllBooks
  	http://localhost:8080/books/getBooksByID/982
  	http://localhost:8080/books/deleteBooksByID/982
  	
  	JPQL
  	http://localhost:8080/books/findBooksByIdJPQL/982
  	
  	Native SQL
  	http://localhost:8080/books/getBooksByIDandAuthorNative/5434/Robert Lafore
  	
  	@NamedQuery
  	http://localhost:8080/books/findBooksByPrice/800
  	
  	
  	
  	
  	
   
   
   